linefit.IO

Interface HasDataToSave

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataSet, GraphArea, LineFit

    public interface HasDataToSave
    This interface should be used for classes and objects that have data that should be saved in the LineFit file. It provides a set of standardized functions to read in data and/or options related to the data from a file line by line and to retrieve all the data and the options related to the data and their settings as strings for saving them.
    Since:
    0.99.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Keith Rice
